ANOVA 1/28/2020

Isabella Grasso

Load libraries

library(tidyverse)
library(broom)

Create data frame

df <- data.frame(B1 = c(13.1, 15.0, 14.0, 14.4,14.0,11.6),
                 B2 = c(16.3, 15.7, 17.2, 14.9, 14.4, 17.2),
                 B3 = c(13.7, 13.9, 12.4, 13.8, 14.9, 13.3),
                 B4 = c(15.7, 13.7, 14.4, 16, 13.9, 14.7),
                 B5 = c(13.5, 13.4, 13.2, 12.7, 13.4, 12.3))
df <- gather(df, "Brand", "Value")

ANOVA

model <- aov(Value ~ Brand, df)
summary(model)
            Df Sum Sq Mean Sq F value   Pr(>F)    
Brand        4  30.86   7.714   8.444 0.000187 ***
Residuals   25  22.84   0.914                     
---
Signif. codes:  0 ‘***’ 0.001 ‘**’ 0.01 ‘*’ 0.05 ‘.’ 0.1 ‘ ’ 1

Residuals

plot(model)

hat values (leverages) are all = 0.1666667
 and there are no factor predictors; no plot no. 5

Tukey

plot(TukeyHSD(model))
